breezit_data.name: Crowne Plaza Foster City
breezit_data.address: Crowne Plaza Foster City-San Mateo, tucked away in Foster City, California, is a modern and sophisticated backdrop for weddings. The site has a remarkable five-story garden atrium with a flowing waterfall that lends a calmness. Perfectly situated close to San Francisco International Airport, it gives visitors from nearby areas as well as from elsewhere simple access. Having hosted weddings for decades, Crowne Plaza Foster City is well-known for its mix of elegance, comfort, and first-rate service, therefore guaranteeing a flawless celebration for couples.
